mdRecord.dcterms:title: Photograph of Congressman Moore with the Barrackville High School senior class
mdRecord.dcterms:description: Congressman Arch A. Moore, Jr. with thirty-two seniors from Barrackville High School. The students are being escorted around Washington, D.C. by Barrackville High Principal Larney Gump, who is first on the right.
